## Why This Matters for Product Owners

This isn't about proving a workflow tool can be clever. It's a working demonstration that **a small, focused automation loop — classify, check, recommend, ask — can measurably shrink the gap between "client raises an issue" and "the right person acts on it,"** without new headcount, new licenses, or a multi-quarter IT project. That gap is where compliance risk and client churn actually live. Closing it is the business case.

